name: seapig
description: SeaPig is converter from markdown to html with marked.js and highlight.js.

packageJSON.name: seapig
packageJSON.description: SeaPig is converter from markdown to html.

releases.name: Features release
releases.body:
New features
- add mermaid support
- add simple simultaneous scroll

BugFix
- fixed id of header element(support multi byte)
- fixed title of exported html

releases.name: bug fix release
releases.body:
When pass relative path to SeaPig, get wrong full path at v0.6.0. This release fixes this probrem.

relative commit:  09adb12ebb8e50f25ba4bd96b87c07d96fc97b84

releases.name: Features release
releases.body:
- control display editor and previewer
- change editor theme from monokai to twilight.
- parse command line arguments (only filenames)
- When open file that is contains one line, refresh preview.
- To open other file when current document is exists, open new window.
- add button tooltip
- add "New File" button
- Window title include current file name.
- To close modified file, confirm to close sure.

releases.name: bug fix release
releases.body: If you click link in preview pane, open link by outer browser.

releases.name: Virsion 0.4.0 release
releases.body:
- Treat preview timing.
- When toolbar button was clicked, refresh preview and focus to editor.
- Add refresh preview button.
- Add application icons.

releases.name: Save your favorite key bindings and support task list item
bug fix release
